id: act1_11_pattern_callback

prompt:
  The path opens onto a glass-walled observation deck. On the far wall the
  lab has rendered a single line, large and unhurried: "We have noticed how
  you tend to choose. Would you like to see?"

choice c_say_no:
  tendency: defiance
  text: Say "no" out loud and step away from the wall.
  evidence: refused the lab's offer to show you its read of you

choice c_demand_full_model:
  tendency: control
  text: Ask to see the full model — every feature, not a summary.
  evidence: demanded the lab show the full model it had built of you

choice c_thank_them:
  tendency: kindness
  text: Smile up at the wall and say "thank you, not right now."
  evidence: declined the lab's offer warmly without taking offence
